### Scuttling

Many-legged, low to the ground, fast and jittery.

```scheme
(motion
  (actor 'scuttler
    (shape 'circle 16)
    (color 80 60 60))
  (on-tick
    (lambda (t)
      (let* ((phase (modulo t 8))
             (x (+ 100 (* t 3)))
             (jitter (* 2 (- (random 5) 2)))
             (y (+ 340 jitter)))
        (entity 'scuttler (at x y))))))
```

*[needs: random in motion context]*

<!-- BUILD: motion lambda needs (random n) for jitter/noise in locomotion -->

If `random` is unavailable, approximate with a hash:

```scheme
(motion
  (actor 'scuttler
    (shape 'circle 16)
    (color 80 60 60))
  (on-tick
    (lambda (t)
      (let* ((phase (modulo t 8))
             (x (+ 100 (* t 3)))
             (jitter (- (modulo (* t 7) 5) 2))
             (y (+ 340 jitter)))
        (entity 'scuttler (at x y))))))
```

[VISUAL: A dark circle scuttles fast and low, y-position jittering ±2 pixels each frame. Insectoid, nervous.]

The jitter breaks the smooth oscillation—many legs never quite synchronize.

